These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 9

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-9-1::.
There are 2 different favourite colors: mauve, grey
The people have 2 different hobbies: gardening, traveling
1. the person who's hobby is traveling is in an odd position##4
2. the person who likes grey and the person who's hobby is traveling have the same parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |    2    |
| Food    | grey | mauve  |
| Sport   | traveling    | gardening |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-9-2::.
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: mystery, martial-arts
2 different pets are kept: frog, hedgehog
1. the person watching mystery movies and the owner of the frog have the same parity positions##9
2. the person watching mystery movies is somewhere to the right of the person watching martial-arts movies##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1     |     2     |
| Beverage   | martial-arts      | mystery       |
| Food       | hedgehog | frog |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-9-3::.
The people have 2 different jobs:  musician, freelancer
There are 2 different favourite beverages: milk, almond-milk
1. the musician and the person drinking milk have different parity positions##9
2. the person drinking almond-milk is on the right of the person drinking milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |
| Music-Genre   | freelancer     | musician       |
| Sport         | milk | almond-milk |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-9-4::.
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: balloon-flower, orchid
City: new-york, paris
1. the person traveling to paris is on the left or right of the person traveling to new-york##3
2. the person who growsorchid and the person traveling to paris have different parity positions##9
3. the person who growsballoon-flower is on the right of the person traveling to new-york##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |
| Nationality   | orchid | balloon-flower |
| Sport         | new-york | paris  |

 #################################

 
